sequenceDiagram
  participant Surface as UI/CLI/MCP/COM/AppIntent
  participant Policy as Policy Engine
  participant Core as fe_reader_core
  participant Workflow as Workflow/Redaction/Metadata
  participant Writer as PDF Writer
  participant Verify as Verification
  participant Receipt as Audit Receipt

  Surface->>Core: FeOperationIntent
  Core->>Policy: evaluate(intent)
  Policy-->>Core: allow/read_only/requires_approval/deny
  Core->>Workflow: plan(intent)
  Workflow-->>Core: FePatchPlan
  Core-->>Surface: plan for review
  Surface->>Core: ApprovalToken + PatchPlanId
  Core->>Writer: apply(plan, write_mode)
  Writer-->>Core: FeApplyResult
  Core->>Verify: verify(result, plan)
  Verify-->>Core: FeVerificationReport
  Core->>Receipt: emit(intent, plan, result, verification)
  Receipt-->>Surface: FeAuditReceipt
